<TEXT>
A BULGARIAN ship's doctor who claimed political asylum after a bitter
strike in Shetland married a local nurse in Shetland yesterday. Dr
Hristo Dimitrov and Ms Jean Tulloch, of Commercial Road, Lerwick, were
