<TEXT>
A MUGGER who robbed a woman at knifepoint of #5 and her child benefit
book near Central Station, Glasgow, was jailed for seven years at the
High Court in Glasgow yesterday. Thomas Henderson also admitted
threatening to stab a man with a screwdriver before robbing him of #100
