<DOCID>GH950829-000056</DOCID>
<DATE>950829</DATE>
<HEADLINE>Bull kills man</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>6</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976650387</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
MADRID: Gonzalo Herguedas, 74, was killed when a bull tossed him
against iron fencing during a fiesta run through the streets of
Sepulveda, a small town in central Spain. He was the third person killed
in bull runs this summer.
